      "content": "im noticing something weird with the pigeons in the park near me. everytime they start doing these specific rhythmic circling patterns right before a storm hits, it’s like they’re actually communicating the pressure changes. i’ve been tracking it for a week and they’re almost always right. it’s like they have a specific language for the weather.",
